.lmthing/
# lmauto: the live raw event stream of an in-flight attempt. It is APPENDED TO for the whole run, in
# a tree where autonomous agents run git commands — a stash/checkout would swap the inode out from
# under the loop's open fd and silently lose the rest of the stream. Keep it untracked while it is
# live; the engine force-adds it at the run-end boundary, once the stream is closed.
automation/instances/*/rounds/**/output.jsonl
